- Run 'diva-Line-ForcedAlignment.sh' to apply forced alingment on just one line image.
	- input: contains the name of text image, and the line number
	- output: probability matrix is found in 'new_proMatrix', aligned results with letter location and word location are found in 'new_alignment'
- Run 'diva-Image-ForcedAlignment.sh' to apply forced alingment on all the line images of a text image.
	- input: contains the name of text image
	- output: probability matrix is found in 'new_proMatrix', aligned results with letter location and word location are found in 'new_alignment'
